{"tid":2496914,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"警世post: 千祈唔好喺叫你自偏電腦公司嘅公司度做","createTime":"2021-04-20T06:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T07:23:21.000Z","uid":27425,"like":38,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"96735433793c647c0d277bac41b7fc3a7eadde91","tid":2496914,"uid":27425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"話說我就喺荃灣Cyberport入面嘅一間橙色logo既公司度做<br />\n公司規模連埋老細都係得個4個人<br />\n<br />\n一開始見工嘅時候，佢叫我哋帶電腦，我都覺得冇所謂，但係做做下，所有公司嘅資料就會係你部電腦入面越積越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後你會覺得，放咗工都好似返緊工一樣，因為公司資料都係你部電腦入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直至今日，有人唔小心搞到我部電腦入哂水，老細完全係覺得公司唔洗負責。因為呢部係你部電腦，所有野都係你personal既錯，公司都唔會幫你claim任何既維修費，一毫子都唔會出，就算你部電腦之前一直都幫公司搵緊錢都好！<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">佢都係唔撚會理你架！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">所以</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">千祈唔好返要你自備電腦既公司</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">到時有咩事，公司都係唔會理</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">叫你帶得都係度鳩縮嘅老細</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">奉勸咁多位FG千祈唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好誤入歧途，入錯公司事小，激撚親自己事大！"},{"pid":"dac76e1c326e35eebe6a3968b5e55b12d8ffd2ee","tid":2496914,"uid":196924,"like":28,"dislike":16,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"睇下你個標題先講啦<br />\n<br />\n咩水平嘅人咪搵到咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0fcb5781b0e695c8e9f3773f277b571916f2fb","tid":2496914,"uid":152598,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dac76e1c326e35eebe6a3968b5e55b12d8ffd2ee","tid":2496914,"uid":196924,"like":28,"dislike":16,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"睇下你個標題先講啦<br />\n<br />\n咩水平嘅人咪搵到咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/do